author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: If you want something, you must say it with your chest or just shoot your shot. Why do y’all go behind the bush? What’s there?

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: This being is so dramatic. 🙄😂

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: He’s dressed so well today and ready to take on the week! 😍🔥

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: Exhausted 😭😭

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: It always feels so weird when I’m working towards a deadline and I finish earlier than anticipated.

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: Taking everyday as it comes and allowing myself to live in the moment. I know God has got my back! 🙏🏼

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: Does anyone know if there’s a live stream for Ndangi’s funeral?

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: Today will be the hardest! God, I ask that you give everyone the strength to take Ndangi to his final resting place. ♥️🙏🏼🕊

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: I don’t think I’ve seen so many people or my friends hurting so much because of the amazing impact you had on their lives Ndangi. 😔🕊

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: That was a beautiful farewell ceremony to Ndangi ♥️🕊🙏🏼

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: Ndangi’s memorial live is not working, 😭😭is anyone else having this problem too?

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: The hurt on the TL hit hard today. 💔My condolences to everyone who lost a friend. I’m left speechless. Fly high 🕊🕊 God has got you protected in Heaven. 🙏🏼

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: At this point I don’t have words.

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: God is, has and continues to be so good! Super grateful! 🙏🏼

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: I can’t emphasize this enough, life really has its ways of teaching you lessons.

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: I’m so glad life has a way of showing you who needs to be apart of your life. It’s actually a blessing.

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: Disappointment after disappointment.

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text:
I felt like I was back in South Africa. 🙄🙄🤦🏽‍♀️🤦🏽‍♀️
The electricity in Klein Windhoek was off for 4 hours. @CoWMunicipality did not say anything about an expected power outage nor say anything on their page when it went out.

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: I wish WhatsApp had a close friends option. 🙄

author: Mutaleni ya Toivo
text: I’m grateful for my parents house and the house we grew up in. It’s beautiful, nothing like anything else I’ve seen in Namibia. 😍
